    <article id="post-2410" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../post/2410.html" rel="bookmark">基于Laravel开发博客应用系列 —— 联系我们 &amp; 发送邮件 &amp; 队列使用（基于数据库）</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-12-07T22:11:46+08:00">2015-12-07</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2015-12-07T22:16:03+08:00">2015-12-07 22:16:03</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    15312 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../post/2410.html#comments">
                        25 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/2410.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/2015-12-07-22-02-26-256x128.png" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/2410.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="1329" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/2015-12-07-22-02-26-1329x200.png" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>本节我们将会添加联系我们功能到博客应用，要实现该功能我们需要了解 Laravel 的邮件发送功能以及队列处理机制。
1、邮件发送设置
为了使用 Laravel 5.1 的邮件发送功能，首选需要配置邮件发送，配置很简单，打开 .env 文件，查看邮件配置部分：
MAIL_DRIVER=smtp
MAIL_HOST=mailtrap.io
MAIL_PORT=2525
MAIL_...</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <footer class="entry-meta">
