            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../post/2320.html" rel="bookmark">基于Laravel开发博客应用系列 —— 在后台实现文章标签增删改查功能</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-12-02T22:10:36+08:00">2015-12-02</time>
