    <article id="post-2249" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../post/2249.html" rel="bookmark">基于 Laravel 开发博客应用系列 —— 从测试开始（二）：使用Gulp实现自动化测试</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-11-29T16:12:12+08:00">2015-11-29</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2015-12-02T17:15:53+08:00">2015-12-02 17:15:53</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    20914 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../post/2249.html#comments">
                        44 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/2249.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/markdown_icon-256x128.png" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/2249.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="600" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/markdown_icon-600x200.png" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>3、使用 Gulp 进行 TDD（测试驱动开发）
Gulp 是一个使用 JavaScript 编写的自动化构建工具。用于对前端通用任务（如最小化、压缩、编译）进行自动构建。Gulp 还可以用来监控源代码的改动并自动运行任务。

Laravel 5.1 提供了一个封装 Gulp 的 Laravel Elixir 包，可用于轻松构建 Gulp 任务，Elixir 为 Gulp 添加了优...</p>
        </div>

